<p><a name="Delivery_semantics" id="Delivery_semantics"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Routing&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Delivery semantics">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Delivery semantics</span></h2>
<table style="float:right; clear:both; margin:1em; padding:0; border: thin solid #000; text-align:center;">
<tr>
<th style="background-color:#ddd; color:#000;">
<p><strong class="selflink">Routing</strong> Schemes</p>
<p><a href="/wiki/File:Cast.svg" class="image" title="Cast.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/cf/Cast.svg/100px-Cast.svg.png" width="100" height="67" border="0" /></a></p>
